<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900731-0059</DOCNO><DOCID>900731-0059.</DOCID><HL>   Litton Gets McDonnell Contract</HL><DATE>07/31/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7</SO><CO>   LIT MD</CO><LP>   BEVERLY HILLS, Calif. -- Litton Industries Inc. said itreceived a two-year contract from St. Louis-based McDonnellDouglas Corp. to develop sensor technology for a fiber-opticflight-control system for advanced aircraft.   The companies didn't disclose the amount of the contract.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>